524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasatch_County,_Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasatch_County,_Utah\"}, {\"begin\": 249, \"end\": 255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadeus_William_Grabau\", \"score\": 0.9999999952229928, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Grabau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadeus_William_Grabau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amadeus_William_Grabau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"local planning efforts\", \"from\": 283, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"the future Olympics\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Largely we have discussed the need for identifying projects that the community views as important that might also have a connection with the Olympics,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"projects\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"the community\", \"from\": 401, \"to\": 414}, {\"ngram\": \"a connection\", \"from\": 455, \"to\": 467}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We hope that the bypass could be in place by then, because I think transportation from Utah County and through Wasatch County is going to be an important aspect of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_County,_Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999310609861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Utah County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_County,_Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_County,_Utah\"}, {\"begin\": 609, \"end\": 623, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasatch_County,_Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999942232307, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wasatch County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/W